在 Device ‘F1’ 中有一字串由大小寫英文字母所組成（字串的結束字元為 ‘$’，其 ASCII 值為 0x24）。請用 SIC 的指令集寫一組合語言程式，完成以下的功能：

請從 Device ‘F1’ 中讀取字串，如果所讀取的字元為小寫，請將其轉換為大寫字元並寫入 Device ‘F2’ 中 （如果所讀取的字元為大寫，則不變，直接寫到 Device ‘F2’ 中）。

完成基本功能者滿分90分，將讀取字元及寫入字元分別以副程式來撰寫者滿分100分。

In device ‘F1’, there is a string that is composed of uppercase and lowercase characters; and the termination character of the string is ‘$’ (its ASCII value is 0x24). Please write a SIC assembler program that completes the following function:

Read characters from device F1. If the character is lowercase, the program translates the character to an uppercase character and write it to device F2. If the character is uppercase, the program writes it to device F2 directly.

You will get 90 points if you complete the above function. If the reading character and the writing character functions are completed by using subroutines, you will get 100 points.

Please upload your program before 23:55, 6 March.